		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Active listening</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>Active listening</b> is an intent to "<a href="/wiki/Hearing_(sense)" title="Hearing (sense)">listen</a> for meaning".</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
<tr>
<td>
